  "body": "In order to remove `Gwei` from config, we'll need to update `base_reward_quotient` to the latest spec.\r\n\r\nLatest spec:\r\n`base_reward_quotient = integer_squareroot(total_balance) // BASE_REWARD_QUOTIENT.`\r\n\r\nWhat we have:\r\n`base_reward_quotient = BASE_REWARD_QUOTIENT * integer_squareroot(total_balance // GWEI_PER_ETH)`",
